# Asset Models Directory

This directory contains Blender-generated 3D models.

## Structure
```
models/
├── creatures/   - Night creatures (ShadowStalker, FissureDweller, NightBird)
├── animals/     - Day/night wildlife
├── structures/  - Buildings, landmarks
├── npcs/        - Survivors, pet companion
├── props/       - Signs, collectibles
└── terrain/     - Fault line edges, cliffs
```

## Note
FBX/OBJ/BLEND files are NOT committed to git.
Run Blender scripts to generate them:

```bash
blender --background --python tools/blender/create_creatures.py
```

See docs/faultline-fear/ASSET_PIPELINE.md for full workflow.
